OL,3,CElizabeth Hurley 'crushed' by
OL,4,Callegation of phone tapping, court told
OL,6,FPrince Harry returned to the Royal
OL,7,FCourts of Justice in London on
OL,8,FThursday for the fourth day of the
OL,9,Ftrial of the legal action against the
OL,10,Fpublisher of the Daily Mail, a day
OL,11,Fafter giving evidence at the High
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FAssociated Newspapers Limited (ANL)
OL,15,Fstrongly denies wrongdoing and is
OL,16,Fdefending the claims.
OL,18,FOn Thursday, Hurley, accompanied by
OL,19,Fher son, Damian, attended court to
OL,20,Fgive evidence.
