OL,6,FHurley said: "There were so many
OL,7,Fdeeply hurtful and damaging articles
OL,8,Fabout me in the media. It became just
OL,9,Fa business of unpleasantness."
OL,11,FHurley also told the court that
OL,12,Fsometimes she would worry if she had
OL,13,Fsaid something too loudly, claiming
OL,14,F"there were microphones on the
OL,15,Fwindowsill of my dining room... I was
OL,16,Fbeing listened to".
OL,18,FHurley said: "Yes, there were leaks,
OL,19,Fbut they were not from my friends."
