OL,6,FIn written submissions for the trial,
OL,7,FAntony White KC, for ANL, said the
OL,8,Fallegations of UIG by Associated's
OL,9,Fjournalists, "including of phone
OL,10,Fhacking and phone tapping, in
OL,11,Fconnection with Ms Hurley or her 10
OL,12,Fnamed associates" are "unsupported by
OL,13,Fthe evidence before the court".
