OL,6,FHe added: "Not only are they entirely
OL,7,Fbaseless but, as with the other
OL,8,Fclaimants' claims, they are borne of
OL,9,Fan attempt by members of the
OL,10,Fclaimants' research team, adopted by
OL,11,FMs Hurley and her legal
OL,12,Frepresentatives, to present a case of
OL,13,FUIG against Associated based entirely
OL,14,Fon spurious and, or, discredited
OL,15,Finformation."
OL,17,FDuring his trial opening, Mr White
OL,18,Fsaid that the claims against the
OL,19,Fpublisher were "threadbare" and had
OL,20,Fbeen brought too late.
